text:
Good burger if your in the mood to wait for it, ox tail chili cheese fries are a must!  Service is mediocre at best
 @Joseph I'm a returning customer but the service issue I have is that it always seems under staffed. 
I feel I'm waiting for service but I don't feel like I'm waiting on the food. Waiting for someone to get to the table  , refill your drink,  if you need something in between , waiting for the check has been my issues every time I have returned.
